## Roadmap
- v0.1: template transforms (this MVP)
- v0.2: add optional LLM augment in core (behind a flag)
- v0.3: connectors (Buffer/Notion/GitHub PR helper)
- v0.4: n8n nodes + Telegram bot adapter
```


